>\n<br />\n大家好，我係呀輝～～～～？！"},{"pid":"237a31aef34179538a268aea4a0640306f5e15f1","tid":2462022,"uid":314611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"搞下笑姐"},{"pid":"0ad5ef8924743d711e5f5e277155017d5774eefd","tid":2462022,"uid":383547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"聽左2秒即stop 唔想繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b238743723bdf6aeb2624cbc54edbdcd863f737","tid":2462022,"uid":173047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"04dd203adc963b01eacd3704e6d59e93fdbcc939","tid":2462022,"uid":24024,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:14:37.000Z","msg":"唔知點解 大部份番開教會嘅人<br />\n講嘢成日都捉錯用神咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識幾個由細教會番到大嘅<br />\n同佢哋講嘢都覺得好撚尷尬<br />\n<br />\n嗰種想show比人睇自己信耶蘇得嚟 都以為自己好潮好in個種呢<br />\n唔知有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"潮呢樣嘢太自我<br />\n唔可以搭其他嘢<br />\n一搭就唔潮<br />\n仲要係老土耶穌嘢"},{"pid":"9a951d11a0968237dbca9222e3bc65f339f38192","tid":2462022,"uid":232167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"04dd203adc963b01eacd3704e6d59e93fdbcc939","tid":2462022,"uid":24024,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:14:37.000Z","msg":"唔知點解 大部份番開教會嘅人<br />\n講嘢成日都捉錯用神咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識幾個由細教會番到大嘅<br />\n同佢哋講嘢都覺得好撚尷尬<br />\n<br />\n嗰種想show比人睇自己信耶蘇得嚟 都以為自己好潮好in個種呢<br />\n唔知有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:30:42.000Z","msg":"周不時做柒野都好有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>都以為自己好潮好in個種呢</blockquote><br />\n呢個更甚，見過有啲人以為自己好yo，點知佢一出聲就dead air<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實冇必要咁樣搭爹<br />\n我亦識得有啲人係有正常社交，更加唔會句句/每個post